data.description: Welcome Home! Well maintained & recently renovated home featuring a fully finished basement. Gleaming hardwood floors throughout the main level with an open concept. Kitchen features SS appliances and overlooks the living room and dining area. Spacious owner's suite features en suite with large shower plus there's an additional bedroom on the upper level. The fully finished basement features a bonus room, 1 full bathroom and 3 additional bedrooms. Spacious deck right off the kitchen backdoor perfect for entertaining, relaxing and looking out onto the large leveled backyard. Great location, move in ready, schedule your tour today!
